AGI -&nbsp;The ancient building of the former Copenhagen Stock Exchange is on fire: a huge fire dropped the spire of 54 meters, symbol of the 17th century palace, which was under renovation. The "Borsen" was built under the reign of Christian IV between 1619 and 1640, and is located near the Danish parliament, the Palace of Christiansborg.
&nbsp;
<div </div
